window.onload -> initialize controls via IIFE
controls:
Tab - Create child
Shift + Tab - create older sibling
Ctrl + Tab - (next tab)
Ctrl + Shift + Tab - (previous tab)
Ctrl + t - (new tab)
Ctrl + Alt + Tab - create dotted arrow > related object state

Enter - Create sibling
Shift + Enter - create new parent
Ctrl + Enter - Create new
Ctrl + Alt + Enter  - Create solid arrow > related object state

Arrow Keys
up - Move to prior sibling
down - Move to next sibling
left - Move to first parent
right - Move to first child

Left Mouse click - select / deselect
Right Mouse click - (open formatter)
Mouse Drag - move selected object / create selection area
Ctrl + Mouse Drag - pan

Scroll up - pan up
Scroll down - pan down
Scroll left - pan left
Scroll right - pan right

Ctrl + Scroll up - zoom in
Ctrl + Scroll down - zoom out

delete - delete selected

Ctrlwq + a - select all

********************
Label State
********************
Esc - switch to Label State
any characters - add characters to label
Ctrl + a - select all

********************
Related Object State
********************
Enter - create new object at present level and connect
Shift + Enter - create new object at parent level and connect
Tab - create new object at child level and connect (this would be a separate line of children from the first)

Left Mouse click - connect to clicked object
Right Mouse click - cancel
Esc - cancel
********************

Save
Load

Copy
Paste

Components:
Solid Arrow
Dotted Arrow
Rounded Rec with text
Child of Rounded Rec with text

States:
Selected

